    <item>
      <title>Testing your changes</title>
      <link>//localhost:1313/docs/contribution-guidelines/testing-changes/</link>
      <pubDate>Mon, 01 Jan 0001 00:00:00 +0000</pubDate>
      <guid>//localhost:1313/docs/contribution-guidelines/testing-changes/</guid>
      <description>&lt;h1 id=&#34;how-to-test-your-changesadditions&#34;&gt;How to Test Your Changes/Additions&lt;a class=&#34;td-heading-self-link&#34; href=&#34;#how-to-test-your-changesadditions&#34; aria-label=&#34;Heading self-link&#34;&gt;&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/h1&gt;&#xA;&lt;h2 id=&#34;install-podmandocker-compose&#34;&gt;Install Podman/Docker Compose&lt;a class=&#34;td-heading-self-link&#34; href=&#34;#install-podmandocker-compose&#34; aria-label=&#34;Heading self-link&#34;&gt;&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/h2&gt;&#xA;&lt;p&gt;You can use either podman-compose or docker-compose for this step&lt;/p&gt;&#xA;&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;NOTE:&lt;/strong&gt; Podman might not work on Mac&amp;rsquo;s&lt;/p&gt;&#xA;&lt;p&gt;&lt;code&gt;pip3 install docker-compose&lt;/code&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&#xA;&lt;p&gt;OR&lt;/p&gt;&#xA;&lt;p&gt;To get latest podman-compose features we need, use this installation command&lt;/p&gt;&#xA;&lt;p&gt;&lt;code&gt;pip3 install https://github.com/containers/podman-compose/archive/devel.tar.gz&lt;/code&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&#xA;&lt;h2 id=&#34;current-list-of-scenario-types&#34;&gt;Current list of Scenario Types&lt;a class=&#34;td-heading-self-link&#34; href=&#34;#current-list-of-scenario-types&#34; aria-label=&#34;Heading self-link&#34;&gt;&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/h2&gt;&#xA;&lt;p&gt;Scenario Types:&lt;/p&gt;&#xA;&lt;ul&gt;&#xA;&lt;li&gt;pod-scenarios&lt;/li&gt;&#xA;&lt;li&gt;node-scenarios&lt;/li&gt;&#xA;&lt;li&gt;zone-outages&lt;/li&gt;&#xA;&lt;li&gt;time-scenarios&lt;/li&gt;&#xA;&lt;li&gt;cerberus&lt;/li&gt;&#xA;&lt;li&gt;cluster-shutdown&lt;/li&gt;&#xA;&lt;li&gt;container-scenarios&lt;/li&gt;&#xA;&lt;li&gt;node-cpu-hog&lt;/li&gt;&#xA;&lt;li&gt;node-io-hog&lt;/li&gt;&#xA;&lt;li&gt;node-memory-hog&lt;/li&gt;&#xA;&lt;li&gt;application-outages&lt;/li&gt;&#xA;&lt;li&gt;syn-flood&lt;/li&gt;&#xA;&lt;li&gt;service-hijacking&lt;/li&gt;&#xA;&lt;/ul&gt;&#xA;&lt;h1 id=&#34;testing-changes-in-krkn-lib&#34;&gt;Testing Changes in Krkn-lib&lt;a class=&#34;td-heading-self-link&#34; href=&#34;#testing-changes-in-krkn-lib&#34; aria-label=&#34;Heading self-link&#34;&gt;&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/h1&gt;&#xA;&lt;h2 id=&#34;create-a-kind-cluster-if-needed&#34;&gt;Create a kind cluster if needed&lt;a class=&#34;td-heading-self-link&#34; href=&#34;#create-a-kind-cluster-if-needed&#34; aria-label=&#34;Heading self-link&#34;&gt;&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/h2&gt;&#xA;&lt;ol&gt;&#xA;&lt;li&gt;&#xA;&lt;p&gt;&lt;a href=&#34;https://kind.sigs.k8s.io/docs/user/quick-start/#installation&#34;&gt;Install kind&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/p&gt;</description>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>Contributions</title>
      <link>//localhost:1313/docs/contribution-guidelines/contribute/</link>
      <pubDate>Mon, 01 Jan 0001 00:00:00 +0000</pubDate>
      <guid>//localhost:1313/docs/contribution-guidelines/contribute/</guid>
      <description>&lt;h1 id=&#34;how-to-contribute&#34;&gt;How to contribute&lt;a class=&#34;td-heading-self-link&#34; href=&#34;#how-to-contribute&#34; aria-label=&#34;Heading self-link&#34;&gt;&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/h1&gt;&#xA;&lt;p&gt;Contributions are always appreciated.&lt;/p&gt;&#xA;&lt;p&gt;How to:&lt;/p&gt;&#xA;&lt;ul&gt;&#xA;&lt;li&gt;&lt;a href=&#34;//localhost:1313/docs/contribution-guidelines/contribute/#pull-request&#34;&gt;Submit Pull Request&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/li&gt;&#xA;&lt;li&gt;&lt;a href=&#34;//localhost:1313/docs/contribution-guidelines/contribute/#squash-commits&#34;&gt;Squash Commits&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/li&gt;&#xA;&lt;li&gt;&lt;a href=&#34;//localhost:1313/docs/contribution-guidelines/contribute/#rebase-with-upstream&#34;&gt;Rebase with Upstream&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/li&gt;&#xA;&lt;/ul&gt;&#xA;&lt;h2 id=&#34;pull-request&#34;&gt;Pull request&lt;a class=&#34;td-heading-self-link&#34; href=&#34;#pull-request&#34; aria-label=&#34;Heading self-link&#34;&gt;&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/h2&gt;&#xA;&lt;p&gt;In order to submit a change or a PR, please fork the project and follow instructions:&lt;/p&gt;&#xA;&lt;div class=&#34;highlight&#34;&gt;&lt;pre tabindex=&#34;0&#34; style=&#34;background-color:#f8f8f8;-moz-tab-size:4;-o-tab-size:4;tab-size:4;&#34;&gt;&lt;code class=&#34;language-bash&#34; data-lang=&#34;bash&#34;&gt;&lt;span style=&#34;display:flex;&#34;&gt;&lt;span&gt;$ git clone http://github.com/&amp;lt;me&amp;gt;/krkn-hub&#xA;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&#34;display:flex;&#34;&gt;&lt;span&gt;$ &lt;span style=&#34;color:#204a87&#34;&gt;cd&lt;/span&gt; krkn-hub&#xA;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&#34;display:flex;&#34;&gt;&lt;span&gt;$ git checkout -b &amp;lt;branch_name&amp;gt;&#xA;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&#34;display:flex;&#34;&gt;&lt;span&gt;$ &amp;lt;make change&amp;gt;&#xA;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&#34;display:flex;&#34;&gt;&lt;span&gt;$ git add &amp;lt;changes&amp;gt;&#xA;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&#34;display:flex;&#34;&gt;&lt;span&gt;$ git commit -a&#xA;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&#34;display:flex;&#34;&gt;&lt;span&gt;$ &amp;lt;insert good message&amp;gt;&#xA;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&#34;display:flex;&#34;&gt;&lt;span&gt;$ git push&#xA;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/code&gt;&lt;/pre&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;h2 id=&#34;squash-commits&#34;&gt;Squash Commits&lt;a class=&#34;td-heading-self-link&#34; href=&#34;#squash-commits&#34; aria-label=&#34;Heading self-link&#34;&gt;&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/h2&gt;&#xA;&lt;p&gt;If there are mutliple commits, please rebase/squash multiple commits&#xA;before creating the PR by following:&lt;/p&gt;</description>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title></title>
      <link>//localhost:1313/docs/contribution-guidelines/getting-started/</link>
      <pubDate>Mon, 01 Jan 0001 00:00:00 +0000</pubDate>
      <guid>//localhost:1313/docs/contribution-guidelines/getting-started/</guid>
      <description>&lt;h1 id=&#34;how-to-contribute&#34;&gt;How to contribute&lt;a class=&#34;td-heading-self-link&#34; href=&#34;#how-to-contribute&#34; aria-label=&#34;Heading self-link&#34;&gt;&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/h1&gt;&#xA;&lt;p&gt;We&amp;rsquo;re excitd to have to consider contributing to our chaos! Contributions are always appreciated.&lt;/p&gt;&#xA;&lt;p&gt;Below is a flow chart of all the krkn related repositories in git. They all build on eachother with krkn-lib being the lowest level of kubernetes based functions&#xA;&lt;img src=&#34;//localhost:1313/assets/images/krkn-repo-flowchart.jpg&#34; alt=&#34;krkn repo flowchart&#34;&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&#xA;&lt;p&gt;How to:&lt;/p&gt;&#xA;&lt;ul&gt;&#xA;&lt;li&gt;&lt;a href=&#34;//localhost:1313/docs/contribution-guidelines/getting-started/#krkn-lib&#34;&gt;Get started with Krkn-lib&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/li&gt;&#xA;&lt;li&gt;&lt;a href=&#34;//localhost:1313/docs/contribution-guidelines/getting-started/#krkn&#34;&gt;Get started with Krkn&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/li&gt;&#xA;&lt;li&gt;&lt;a href=&#34;//localhost:1313/docs/contribution-guidelines/getting-started/#krkn-hub&#34;&gt;Get started with Krkn-hub&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/li&gt;&#xA;&lt;/ul&gt;&#xA;&lt;h2 id=&#34;krkn-lib&#34;&gt;Krkn-lib&lt;a class=&#34;td-heading-self-link&#34; href=&#34;#krkn-lib&#34; aria-label=&#34;Heading self-link&#34;&gt;&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/h2&gt;&#xA;&lt;p&gt;Clone the repository:&lt;/p&gt;&#xA;&lt;pre tabindex=&#34;0&#34;&gt;&lt;code&gt;git clone https://github.com/krkn-chaos/krkn-lib&#xA;cd krkn-lib&#xA;&lt;/code&gt;&lt;/pre&gt;&lt;p&gt;Make any necessary changes under &lt;code&gt;src/krkn_lib&lt;/code&gt;&#xA;Add tests for new changes in &lt;code&gt;src/krkn_lib/tests&lt;/code&gt;&lt;/p&gt;</description>
    </item>
